Forget about the cheating part, it doesn‚Äôt matter... If you want my honest advice, seems like you already have everything figured out. Listen to your gut. Getting drunk is NOT an excuse. And to me is just not right to sleep with someone hours after a break up, and the horrible things he said to you via messenger, that just shows he doesn‚Äôt appreciate you. 

If things got out of control with his ex, is because they both let that happen, and decided to go with the flow... Why? Because they were drunk? Nah... Lame excuse.

I also think is important not to fight or hate him, we got to remember we are all humans and we are not perfect, walk away like a lady with your head up high and knowing that someone much better will come. So, cmon! You got it girl. :) good luck.
